{"tid":1771420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中立最自私","createTime":"2019-12-06T00:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T01:09:25.000Z","uid":90800,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0db805fc252033bc4fc90b6fb392302dbe959c","tid":1771420,"uid":90800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:47:11.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見<br />\n黑白是良知<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中立最自私</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係大是大非既時候<br />\n仲要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">話自己係中立既人/舖</span></span></strong><br />\n絕對係想獨善其身<br />\n呢種人/舖絕對<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">會因利益而隨時改變立場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以, 如果有人同你講, 我冇任何立場/我中立/政府乜乜乜,但示威者乜乜乜. 麻煩大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">同佢講聲: 嘩!原來你咁自私嫁</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">128 下午3點 維園見</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"53aefab23536b6dc2e43aaa98cdc5ec7a3016ba8","tid":1771420,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:50:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32ecbaf7a1469f0588f4256c2cf34d0c50dc6489","tid":1771420,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2c23f1678e9c71994e69e8a62e6f7276c05167c","tid":1771420,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:50:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c93722531d68d994a34450ebfc3f7d0f799e7458","tid":1771420,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d40959297ff2f78ac276a3e8e8cb27985cfb4a9","tid":1771420,"uid":90800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c93722531d68d994a34450ebfc3f7d0f799e7458","tid":1771420,"uid":321674,"like"